Install ttyd, the gotty alternative

Source:  https://github.com/tsl0922/ttyd
Wiki:    https://github.com/tsl0922/ttyd/wiki
Theme:   https://xtermjs.org/docs/api/terminal/interfaces/itheme/
Options: https://xtermjs.org/docs/api/terminal/interfaces/iterminaloptions/

Theme:

  theme='{"background": "white", "foreground": "black", "selection": "#ccc", "cursor": "blue" }'
  ttyd --port 3000 -t fontSize=20 \
    -t theme="$theme" \
    bash
